# Pops Marketing Website Main Branch Convention

For work scoped to the Pops marketing website in `apps/pops-website/**`, use `main` as the source-of-truth branch and push completed changes only to `origin/main` unless the user explicitly says otherwise.

Do not create, publish, or push feature branches for Pops marketing website work unless the user explicitly asks for a branch or PR.

Before pushing, pull with rebase from `origin/main` and resolve any conflicts:

```shell
git pull --rebase origin main
git push origin main
```
